<subSubSection pageId="19" pageNumber="136" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="19.[151,1436,1343,1910]" pageId="19" pageNumber="136">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,297,1343,1368]" pageId="19" pageNumber="136">Description.</emphasis>
Body (
<figureCitation box="[381,448,1343,1367]" captionStart="FIGURE 2. a – d" captionStartId="8.[151,250,1574,1597]" captionTargetBox="[185,1407,567,1535]" captionTargetId="figure@8.[172,1415,555,1552]" captionTargetPageId="8" captionText="FIGURE 2. a – d. Kapsa (Rigida) furcata Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov.; e – h. Kapsa (Rigida? imminuta Yang &amp; Zhang sp. nov.; i – l. Kapsa (Rigida? megaprocessa Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov.; m – p. Kapsa (Rigida) serrata Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/222872/files/figure.png" pageId="19" pageNumber="136">
Fig. 
<quantity box="[434,448,1343,1367]" metricMagnitude="0" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.0" pageId="19" pageNumber="136" unit="m" value="2.0">2</quantity>
</figureCitation>
m, n) yellow-whitish. Coronal suture (
<figureCitation box="[882,950,1343,1367]" captionStart="FIGURE 2. a – d" captionStartId="8.[151,250,1574,1597]" captionTargetBox="[185,1407,567,1535]" captionTargetId="figure@8.[172,1415,555,1552]" captionTargetPageId="8" captionText="FIGURE 2. a – d. Kapsa (Rigida) furcata Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov.; e – h. Kapsa (Rigida? imminuta Yang &amp; Zhang sp. nov.; i – l. Kapsa (Rigida? megaprocessa Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov.; m – p. Kapsa (Rigida) serrata Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/222872/files/figure.png" pageId="19" pageNumber="136">
Fig. 
<number box="[935,950,1343,1367]" pageId="19" pageNumber="136" value="2.0">2</number>
</figureCitation>
o) obvious, exceeding midlength of vertex. Face (
<figureCitation box="[219,285,1379,1403]" captionStart="FIGURE 2. a – d" captionStartId="8.[151,250,1574,1597]" captionTargetBox="[185,1407,567,1535]" captionTargetId="figure@8.[172,1415,555,1552]" captionTargetPageId="8" captionText="FIGURE 2. a – d. Kapsa (Rigida) furcata Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov.; e – h. Kapsa (Rigida? imminuta Yang &amp; Zhang sp. nov.; i – l. Kapsa (Rigida? megaprocessa Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov.; m – p. Kapsa (Rigida) serrata Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/222872/files/figure.png" pageId="19" pageNumber="136">
Fig. 
<number box="[271,285,1379,1403]" pageId="19" pageNumber="136" value="2.0">2</number>
</figureCitation>
p) short.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="19.[151,1436,1343,1910]" pageId="19" pageNumber="136">
Abdominal apodemes (
<figureCitation box="[460,539,1418,1442]" captionStart="FIGURE 13" captionStartId="20.[151,250,1082,1105]" captionTargetBox="[187,1400,212,1050]" captionTargetId="figure@20.[171,1415,193,1061]" captionTargetPageId="20" captionText="FIGURE 13. Kapsa (Rigida) serrata Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov. a. abdominal apodemes; b. genital capsule; c. pygofer dorsal appendage and anal tube appendage, lateral view; d. subgenital plate, dorsal view; e. paramere, dorsal view; f. connective; g. aedeagus, lateral view; h. aedeagus, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/222883/files/figure.png" pageId="19" pageNumber="136">
Fig. 
<number box="[512,539,1418,1442]" pageId="19" pageNumber="136" value="13.0">13</number>
</figureCitation>
a) short, extend to the 
<number box="[792,806,1418,1442]" pageId="19" pageNumber="136" value="4.0">4</number>
th sternite. Anal tube appendage (
<figureCitation box="[1174,1254,1418,1442]" captionStart="FIGURE 13" captionStartId="20.[151,250,1082,1105]" captionTargetBox="[187,1400,212,1050]" captionTargetId="figure@20.[171,1415,193,1061]" captionTargetPageId="20" captionText="FIGURE 13. Kapsa (Rigida) serrata Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov. a. abdominal apodemes; b. genital capsule; c. pygofer dorsal appendage and anal tube appendage, lateral view; d. subgenital plate, dorsal view; e. paramere, dorsal view; f. connective; g. aedeagus, lateral view; h. aedeagus, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/222883/files/figure.png" pageId="19" pageNumber="136">
Fig. 
<number box="[1226,1254,1418,1442]" pageId="19" pageNumber="136" value="13.0">13</number>
</figureCitation>
b, c) with apical half slim.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="19.[151,1436,1343,1910]" pageId="19" pageNumber="136">
Pygofer dorsal appendage (
<figureCitation box="[503,583,1490,1514]" captionStart="FIGURE 13" captionStartId="20.[151,250,1082,1105]" captionTargetBox="[187,1400,212,1050]" captionTargetId="figure@20.[171,1415,193,1061]" captionTargetPageId="20" captionText="FIGURE 13. Kapsa (Rigida) serrata Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov. a. abdominal apodemes; b. genital capsule; c. pygofer dorsal appendage and anal tube appendage, lateral view; d. subgenital plate, dorsal view; e. paramere, dorsal view; f. connective; g. aedeagus, lateral view; h. aedeagus, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/222883/files/figure.png" pageId="19" pageNumber="136">
Fig. 
<number box="[555,583,1490,1514]" pageId="19" pageNumber="136" value="13.0">13</number>
</figureCitation>
b, c) straight, knife-shaped. Subgenital plate (
<figureCitation box="[1089,1169,1490,1514]" captionStart="FIGURE 13" captionStartId="20.[151,250,1082,1105]" captionTargetBox="[187,1400,212,1050]" captionTargetId="figure@20.[171,1415,193,1061]" captionTargetPageId="20" captionText="FIGURE 13. Kapsa (Rigida) serrata Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov. a. abdominal apodemes; b. genital capsule; c. pygofer dorsal appendage and anal tube appendage, lateral view; d. subgenital plate, dorsal view; e. paramere, dorsal view; f. connective; g. aedeagus, lateral view; h. aedeagus, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/222883/files/figure.png" pageId="19" pageNumber="136">
Fig. 
<number box="[1141,1169,1490,1514]" pageId="19" pageNumber="136" value="13.0">13</number>
</figureCitation>
b, d) with 
<number box="[1282,1296,1490,1514]" pageId="19" pageNumber="136" value="4.0">4</number>
macrosetae, with numerous stout microsetae subbasally. Paramere (
<figureCitation box="[784,867,1526,1550]" captionStart="FIGURE 13" captionStartId="20.[151,250,1082,1105]" captionTargetBox="[187,1400,212,1050]" captionTargetId="figure@20.[171,1415,193,1061]" captionTargetPageId="20" captionText="FIGURE 13. Kapsa (Rigida) serrata Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov. a. abdominal apodemes; b. genital capsule; c. pygofer dorsal appendage and anal tube appendage, lateral view; d. subgenital plate, dorsal view; e. paramere, dorsal view; f. connective; g. aedeagus, lateral view; h. aedeagus, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/222883/files/figure.png" pageId="19" pageNumber="136">
Fig. 
<number box="[839,867,1526,1550]" pageId="19" pageNumber="136" value="13.0">13</number>
</figureCitation>
e) bifurcated apically, ventral branch shorter than dorsal branch. Connective (
<figureCitation box="[478,563,1562,1586]" captionStart="FIGURE 13" captionStartId="20.[151,250,1082,1105]" captionTargetBox="[187,1400,212,1050]" captionTargetId="figure@20.[171,1415,193,1061]" captionTargetPageId="20" captionText="FIGURE 13. Kapsa (Rigida) serrata Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov. a. abdominal apodemes; b. genital capsule; c. pygofer dorsal appendage and anal tube appendage, lateral view; d. subgenital plate, dorsal view; e. paramere, dorsal view; f. connective; g. aedeagus, lateral view; h. aedeagus, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/222883/files/figure.png" pageId="19" pageNumber="136">
Fig. 
<number box="[536,563,1562,1586]" pageId="19" pageNumber="136" value="13.0">13</number>
</figureCitation>
f) with lateral arms long, manubrium short. Aedeagal shaft (
<figureCitation box="[1292,1379,1562,1586]" captionStart="FIGURE 13" captionStartId="20.[151,250,1082,1105]" captionTargetBox="[187,1400,212,1050]" captionTargetId="figure@20.[171,1415,193,1061]" captionTargetPageId="20" captionText="FIGURE 13. Kapsa (Rigida) serrata Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov. a. abdominal apodemes; b. genital capsule; c. pygofer dorsal appendage and anal tube appendage, lateral view; d. subgenital plate, dorsal view; e. paramere, dorsal view; f. connective; g. aedeagus, lateral view; h. aedeagus, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/222883/files/figure.png" pageId="19" pageNumber="136">
Fig. 
<quantity box="[1350,1379,1562,1586]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="kg" metricValue="1.3" pageId="19" pageNumber="136" unit="g" value="13.0">13</quantity>
</figureCitation>
g, h) relatively broad, denticulate dorsoapically, with serrated, compressed protrusion ventrally; dorsal apodeme well developed, preatrium short; gonopore apical, ventral.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="19.[151,1436,1343,1910]" box="[199,677,1670,1694]" pageId="19" pageNumber="136">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,371,1670,1694]" pageId="19" pageNumber="136">Measurement.</emphasis>
